4. cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) - The paper involves computing Laplace-Beltrami eigenfunctions, which is a numerical problem. 
5. cs.SD (Sound) - This is the least likely category, but the paper does mention the use of Laplace-Beltrami eigenspace in sound analysis.
